AUDIO: 'is so much cleaner. And it just takes a&nbsp; couple seconds to pull off. It is so fast&nbsp;&nbsp; I had to slow it down for you to actually&nbsp; see what is happening. Absolute magic. And&nbsp;&nbsp;'

